title: Biggest NFL Free Agency Storylines with Brady Quinn (Football 3/15)
description:
Will Brinson and Brady Quinn break down the biggest storylines from the last several days of free agency, including (surprise!) a rant about the Giants and a debate about their plan. NOTE: This was recorded before Jordy Nelson was released by the Raiders.
